"Verkaufsauftrag, Lead/Verkaufschance usw.)."

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/getting_started/first_campaign.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Filter`: this field provides numerous configurable criteria that "
